title.rendered: JC GOLF SELECTS TAMBOURINE FOR DIGITAL MARKETING STRATEGY

content.rendered:
FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla., May 24, 2023 /PRNewswire/ — JC Golf, the California-based golf management company, selected Tambourine, the Fort Lauderdale-headquartered hospitality digital marketing firm, for custom website design and paid media services to promote its portfolio of high-end courses, JC Player Cards, and membership options.

JC Golf launched its new Tambourine-custom-designed website in January 2023.

Originally published at https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/jc-golf-selects-tambourine-for-digital-marketing-strategy-301832793.html
Images courtesy of https://pixabay.com
